        <h3><a href="~/Home/CheckBalance">Check Balances</a></h3>
        <p>Not sure how much you owe? Click here to view your outstanding balances.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-grow-0">
        <h3><a href="~/Home/AddReview">Write a Review</a></h3>
        <p>Love one of our movies? Click here to write a review!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-grow-0">
        <h3><a href="~/Home/ReviewList">Read Reviews</a></h3>
        <p>Looking for a suggestion? Click here to read our user's movie reviews.</p>
    </div>
